Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:33.21,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still not certain, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,To be a priestess, and to go out and fight... 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.60,0:02:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I are completely different in every way. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.83,0:02:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But in one respect, we're just the same. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.61,0:02:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up, Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.84,0:02:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, to the port hangar! Hurry! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.32,0:02:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamiina, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Simoun is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we're here for, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:59.88,Titles,,0,0,0,,The Hearing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They took my sister hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make them suffer for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't bear to see everyone's feelings torn apart again! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}I'm{\i0} scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The one way Neviril and I are the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is, from now on I'm Neviril's pair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to level the ship off{** off?} for a moment! The Simoun are taking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But Rubor and Caput were both destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Chor Tempest that's launching!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,While Chor Tempest is taking off, bring the ship level and return fire!  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about your aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just pour it into them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was Amuria's and mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they've fixed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Sibylla Aurea's auriga now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Be worthy of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it, our guns aren't hitting them at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,With that kind of aiming, of course they aren't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going in, Yun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To your left!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Diamond Ri Maajon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Diamond Ri Maajon up, the enemy can't hurt us. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, out of all the defensive Ri Maajons, this one is particularly effective. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship's helical motors are barely functioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Will we have to let them tow us back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest will come through!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep the Diamond Ri Maajon going,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and withdraw from the enemy warship's bombardment range.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The hearing is set for this afternoon, as soon as we arrive. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,While we have the opportunity, I'd like to go over the situation with you one more time, Sibylla Neviril.  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father, Halconf, is going to meet us there. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I are completely different in every way. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But in one respect, we're just the same. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up, Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Neviril's gonna come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if she did, what good would it do? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally got twelve people together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I had hoped we would finally all be able to fly together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean anyone still blames you, Mamiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And Dominura's gone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Limone, do you know where she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Neviril does come back, that won't mean Chor Tempest can stay together. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that we can all be present when it's dissolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so this is where you guys are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibyllae of Chor Tempest, the ceremony is about to begin. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make your preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It is regrettable that the task proved to be beyond your abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give me more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest still has great potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.01,0:09:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril has returned, and the new recruits, Limone and Aaeru... 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:10:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that their latent ability surpasses that of all previous sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Limone is that pet sibylla of yours from your report, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Two other sibyllae, Sibylla Mamiina and Sibylla Yun, 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,were transferred to Chor Tempest under Halconf's sponsorship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you tell us, they're about to decide everything in there. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the circumstances, wouldn't it be better to simply proceed to Plan B as quickly as possible? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But aren't they the ones who let those Highlander agents aboard the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0}? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dominura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.31,0:10:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This conversation is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm doing this for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And for your own, too, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It is true that Chor Tempest has many glorious achievements to its name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,However, its own members have rendered those achievements meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They are priestesses of Tempus Spatium, and yet they insulted and fought with one another, 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,putting on a shameful display which demonstrates a complete lack of discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about {\i1}our{\i0} responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We never saw that the peace conference was a ruse,\Nand we allowed dangerous enemy agents to get aboard. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.22,0:11:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Chor Tempest that rescued the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0} from the trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:12:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If it hadn't been for them, I wouldn't be standing here today. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Sibylla Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You have not been given permission to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Onashia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I still clearly remember Erii's cries of grief. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let everyone hear what you have to say. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We are priestesses serving Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We hear the voices of the Simoun, and we draw Ri Maajons in the sky. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Soldiers from neighbouring countries have been invading our Holy Land of Simulacrum,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and we have killed a great many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Slaughtered" them, you might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When we first encountered the air fleet from the Archipelago, in that battle... 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That was not a "battle!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,For a sibylla to speak such words—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...we lost three of our beloved companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,From Chor Caput, eleven sibyllae gave their lives. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A Highland priestess gave her life in a destructive plot against the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0}, 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.41,0:14:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,taking the lives of even more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no falsehood in that girl's devotion to her god.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,As fellow priestesses, what are we supposed to think about that? What should we do?  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, what we're doing is fighting the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now we must say a painful farewell to friends whom we remember so fondly. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They... were our travelling companions. Our comrades in battle.  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we are at war,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,their leaving on this journey was sudden and unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our real job, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Offering perfect Ri Maajons to Tempus Spatium?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Their departure leaves a great hole in our hearts that we cannot fill.  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We've returned to our true duties, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But somehow, it doesn't feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:15:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You mean you {\i1}wanted{\i0} to do funeral ceremonies for the dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And perhaps it should never be filled.  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't what I meant at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our last Ri Maajon as Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite our sadness and loneliness at losing them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It is our duty to carry on. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we even have the right to do their funeral ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a matter of right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Paraietta,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,please offer the memorial ceremony for these comrades who have sacrificed their lives for their countrymen. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We offer the Ri Maajon of the Fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to lay blame for these days of fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been painful and heartbreaking, and perhaps this is fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It may even be the will of Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But right now, I don't care what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I don't care about "the will of God."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have one question I'd like to ask you all:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In spite of that... am I still a Simoun sibylla? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.81,0:16:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril, despite your misgivings, 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you will remain a Simoun sibylla for as long as you wish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The things you have said are inexcusable!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,To say you do not care about the divine will...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot simply allow that to pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, I have something to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from Chor Rubor, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Vyura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked her to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Guragief! To abuse your position on this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you wish to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Vyura, please speak to us. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.94,0:17:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Onashia...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the other Simoun sibyllae love and respect Chor Tempest. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're proud of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the best choir of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of all Simoun sibyllae,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I request that Chor Tempest remain in service.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean the Chor Tempest who act as priestesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,or the Chor Tempest who "fight" in "battle" as a unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Which Chor Tempest is it that you want us to keep?  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They are twelve sibyllae who form pairs and draw Ri Maajons in the sky.  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:18:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There can be only one Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Three o'clock level!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen anything like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they some kind of new artillery shell? Then—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Those aren't shells!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They're heading straight for the Grand Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll destroy them with a Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn them all, every single one of them! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like they just {\i1}want{\i0} us to suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"Us?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So it comes to this after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still doing a Ri Maajon. That hasn't changed at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamiina! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.27,0:20:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,With that many of them, only the Iron Ri Maajon will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible! We need all six Simoun to do the Iron Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The Iron Ri Maajon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:20:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What a lovely breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Vyura!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.03,0:21:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have some good news: Chor Tempest will go on. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.47,0:21:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great, Mamiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.27,0:21:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can keep flying Simoun with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.03,0:21:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great, Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We can keep flying together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.96,0:21:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What could have happened at Headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, something sure happened, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.16,0:21:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril! Vyura!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.38,0:21:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,With Chor Tempest's survival decided, {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0} should be repaired right away. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.49,0:21:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted you to move on with your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You embarrassed a lot of council members back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't just let Chor Tempest carry on as it did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.58,0:22:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,While the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0} is being repaired, Chor Tempest will be stationed aboard the {\i1}Messis{\i0}. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You will fly patrols and reconnaissance missions near the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.68,0:22:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... you mean we're going to fly on {\i1}that{\i0} thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.50,0:22:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a little...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.84,0:22:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get greedy. We're lucky they're letting Chor Tempest survive at all. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.25,0:22:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great. Even the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.30,0:22:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not complaining at all!
